### Test WebSocket Notification System
### Base URL
@baseUrl = http://localhost:3000
@token = YOUR_JWT_TOKEN_HERE

### 1. Get unread notifications
GET {{baseUrl}}/notifications/unread
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 2. Send test notification
